          <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-semibold text-navy">Weight</td>
          <td class="py-3">2,000 Lbs</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- Summary -->
  <h2 id="summary">Summary</h2>

  <p>
    A tramp oil centrifuge is ideal for the efficient and continuous removal of tramp oil from water-based machine coolant. The comparatively higher initial cost is justified by the improved product quality, reduced part rejections, longer tool life, less machine tool downtime, and safe working conditions.
  </p>

  <p>
    Ready to discuss tramp oil removal for your facility? Contact Dolphin Centrifuge at <a href="tel:+12485222573">(248) 522-2573</a> or <a href="mailto:sales@dolphincentrifuge.com">sales@dolphincentrifuge.com</a>. You can also explore our <a href="/industrial-centrifuge-sample-testing/">sample testing service</a> to verify separation performance before purchasing.
  </p>

